id Marcos in a mix of Filipino and English.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.015992884189637e-14, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"an easy feat\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"Marcos\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"a mix\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"Filipino\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"English\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is an extremely difficult achievement to have managed.\\\"\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an extremely difficult achievement\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marcos acknowledged that the rewards are not enough to compensate for the hardships the Philippines' latest set of Olympians have undergone.\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.015992884189637e-14, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marcos\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"the rewards\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardships\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I apologize if it is just a small amount.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a small amount\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know that P1 million is small if you compare it to your sacrifice and the experiences you went through.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sacrifice\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for now, this is what we will do,\\\" said Marcos.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marcos\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Celebrating its100th yearof Olympic participation, the Philippines enjoyed itsall-time best campaignas it won multiple gold medals in a single edition for the first time and matched its biggest medal haul in history.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.015992884189637e-14, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its100th yearof Olympic participation\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"itsall-time best campaignas\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple gold medals\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"a single edition\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"its biggest medal haul\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Philippines finished tied with Hong Kong for 37th place in themedal tallyfor its highest Olympic ranking since 1964 and emerged as thebest performing Southeast Asian nation.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.015992884189637e-14, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\":